snippet.title: BIONICLE: Masks of Power Environmental Teaser (Coming to Steam)
snippet.description:
Team Kanohi presents the first look at the environments of BIONICLE: Masks of Power, a project 5 years in the making!

BIONICLE: Masks of Power is an Open-World action/adventure fan-game set in the world of BIONICLE.
(This trailer represents the game in development. All areas are subject to change.)

Find the power, relive the legend, at https://masksofpower.com/

Visit our Steam page here! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1704850

Discord: https://discord.gg/7G4whrK
Twitter: https://twitter.com/masksofpower
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/masksofpower/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MasksOfPower/
